content.raw_html:
1. The following forms shall be in the form approved by the Minister:

1.  An application for an extra-provincial licence.

2.  An appointment of an agent for service or a revised appointment of an agent for service.

3.  An application for an amendment to an extra-provincial licence.

4.  An application for termination of an extra-provincial licence.  O. Reg. 245/05, s. 1.

 

Français
